T02TD2468E:141b-1: sva tsitta yo gi grantha ka to pa de sha / bod skad du /
T02TD2468E:142a-1: gi sems mdud pa 'grol ba'i man ngag bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2468E:142a-2: ae ma ho gdod nas ma skyes pa //
T02TD2468E:142a-4: gzhan min rang gi snying dbus gnas //
T02TD2468E:142a-5: bla ma'i zhal las shes par 'gyur //
T02TD2468E:142a-6: kye ho bzhin bzang nga la nyon //
T02TD2468E:142a-7: gang gis 'ching bar byed pa'i rgyu //
T02TD2468E:142a-8: de nyid grol bar byed pa'i lam //
T02TD2468E:142a-10: rmi lam grong khyer yangs pa na //
T02TD2468E:142a-11: sgyu ma'i skyes bu longs spyod pa //
T02TD2468E:142a-12: longs spyod dus na longs spyod med //
T02TD2468E:142a-13: snang sems de ltar shes par bya //
T02TD2468E:142a-14: sna tshogs snang ba rang gi sems //
T02TD2468E:142a-15: de ni sprul pa'i tshogs 'dus bzhin //
T02TD2468E:142a-16: rang sems dbang po'i gzhu 'dra ba //
T02TD2468E:142a-17: gnyug ma 'od gsal lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2468E:142a-18: gang shar thams cad de yin te //
T02TD2468E:142a-19: de ni gang du'ang ma shar ba'o//
T02TD2468E:142a-20: de phyir gang skyes de ma skyes //
T02TD2468E:142a-21: ma skyes pa nyid skye ba'i tshul //
T02TD2468E:142a-22: me long gzugs dang pi wang sgra //
T02TD2468E:142a-23: dge slong sprul pa rdzu 'phrul bzhin //
T02TD2468E:142a-24: yod dang med dang skye 'gag dang //
T02TD2468E:142a-26: sgyu ma yi ni rta glang ltar //
T02TD2468E:142a-28: de nyid ston gyi mkha' bzhin du //
T02TD2468E:142a-29: 'od gsal chos gsum sbyar bar bya //
T02TD2468E:142a-30: ae ma'o rnal 'byor rgyal po che //
T02TD2468E:142a-31: ae ma'o ma bcings ma grol ba'o //
T02TD2468E:142a-32: ae ma'o ma spangs lhun gyis grub //
T02TD2468E:142a-33: ae ma'o ae ma'o bde ba che //
T02TD2468E:142a-34: ma rtogs 'gro la rang dbang du //
T02TD2468E:142a-35: snying rje chen po'i dbang gis na //
T02TD2468E:142a-36: dmigs med rnam kun yongs rdzogs pa'i //
T02TD2468E:142a-37: bsod nams ye shes phun tshogs 'gyur //
T02TD2468E:142a-38: rang gi sems kyi mdud pa 'grol ba'i gdams pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2468E:142a-40: // / bla ma'i mi tra a'a na nda zhes bya ba sbas pa'i sangs rgyas de nyid bod yul kha ba can gyi mthil bkra shis kyi tshong 'dus chen po 'gur mo rin po che'i gling du byon pa'i tshe mong sngags kyi bdag po chen po //
T02TD2468E:142a-46: gshen drug gis zhus pa'i don du gsungs pa /
T02TD2468E:142a-47: phyag rgya chen po tshig chod kyi do ha gnubs lo ts'a bas bsgyur ba'o//
